data.description:
Sellers are offering $5,000 towards closing costs or a rate buy down!!
Welcome to this charming home nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac. This beautifully well maintained property offers comfort & convenience in every corner. This home has undergone a huge transformation, with a new HVAC(2 units), kitchen, living room, dining room, all bathrooms, and master bedroom all meticulously remodeled to perfection. Including knotty alder trim and doors downstairs. All fresh paint inside and outside. With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this home provides ample space & storage for your family. Step into the heart of the home and be greeted by a brand-new kitchen, top-of-the-line appliances, double oven, granite countertops and new cabinets with an abundant storage. The open-concept design creates a great space for entertaining! Retreat to the master bedroom and indulge in the newly renovated en-suite bathroom. Walk outside through the two large sliding doors to enjoy the spacious backyard ideal for entertaining with built in speakers inside and outside. Located in the backyard is a 180sqft shed on a concreate slab with power ran to it. You will love watching the sunsets looking over the greenbelt. The housing addition has a neighborhood large pool for these hot summers. Conveniently located near restaurants & shopping. This home comes with soooo much more. It is a must-see. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful property your own!
